Finally, I get to see all those episodes I missed because my parents thought I was too young to watch them.  Very pleased with this collection and so far, all the discs played without incident.  I had forgotten about how Hitchcock did humorous intros and played up the role of the show sponsors.  What a real treat!
Timely delivery, I've been really enjoying these old episodes.

Very high quality reproduction of a classic old TV show with great stories portrayed by the best of the best actors/actresses.  And no commercials! What more could you want?

Not exactly cheap, but since I cut the cable 10 years ago I have lots of bucks to spend on TV entertainment.- stuff I want to watch, when I want to watch it.

Great old classics.  Love Alfred's intros and closings.  Has a distinct dry humor that is great.  Stories are fun to watch.

What is not to love? Five great seasons from the Master of Suspense, featuring stories by some of the more famous television writers of the day and starring actors and actresses who have become legends in the annals of pop culture. Bought at a great price, I had happy to pass my Season One that I already owned to one of my best friends.

Good collection of the 30-minute Hitchcock TV series.  Not much bonus material, but that is not important to me.  Also, all the DVDs played without a problem, which I have found is not always true of box set offerings.  For that reason, I now test all the disks before the Amazon return window closes.

It is very good.  The picture quality is great.  The best part is that the commercials are removed of course, making it more enjoyable to see.  A bonus is that you can see a bunch of future stars in lead and cameo roles.
I recall as a kid watching Alfred Hitchcock with my parents, there was only 1 tv in our house ... I love those shows. such suspense, great mysteries, must see, brings back such great memories.

I opened the box to look at the DVDs and choose one to start watching. I was horrified to discover that they look like there were used for a very aggressive, impromptu hockey game! Broken plastic, torn and battered boxes that hold the disks, etc. At this price, it really is a huge letdown. Buy at your own risk.
Great collection.  Waiting for Season 7 to become available.
Love this old black and white classics. I only wish they had more seasons in one collection. Noticed that some risks have a side A and B while others do not.
